<lb n="0919c03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0919006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note>佛說如意摩尼陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0919c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0919c05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0919007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（西天…臣））二十字＝（（三藏法師））四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><note n="0919007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣）二十字＝（三藏法師）四字【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0919007"><lem wit="【大】">西天<note n="0919008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔譯經〕－【明】</note><app n="0919008"><lem wit="【大】">譯經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿
<lb n="0919c06" ed="T"/>傳法大師<note n="0919009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0919009"><lem wit="【大】">臣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">三藏法師</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">宋西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少卿傳法大師臣</rdg></app>施護奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0919c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919c0701">如是我聞。一時佛在舍衛國迦利哩城。爾時
<lb n="0919c08" ed="T"/>世尊告尊者阿難。今有陀羅尼能除一切暴
<lb n="0919c09" ed="T"/>惡雷電。汝當受持。此隨求如意寶經。過去如
<lb n="0919c10" ed="T"/>來應正等覺親所宣說。我今亦說。於其世間
<lb n="0919c11" ed="T"/>行大悲愍。利益安樂天上人間一切有情。阿
<lb n="0919c12" ed="T"/>難白言唯然世尊。願樂欲聞我今受持。佛告
<lb n="0919c13" ed="T"/>阿難汝等。當知東方有雷電名曰阿伽。南方
<lb n="0919c14" ed="T"/>有雷電名曰設帝嚕。西方有雷電名曰哆&CB00425;
<lb n="0919c15" ed="T"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>婆。北方有雷電名曰掃那摩&CB00135;。阿難若
<lb n="0919c16" ed="T"/>有善男子善女人。知此雷電名號及住處方
<lb n="0919c17" ed="T"/>位。一切雷電不怖彼人。若所在之處書寫此
<lb n="0919c18" ed="T"/>雷電名號。受持供養。一切雷電而不能傷。爾
<lb n="0919c19" ed="T"/>時世尊說此擁護真言章句。</p>
<lb n="0919c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919c2001" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;彌&CB00135;彌&CB00135;彌孕<note place="inline">二合</note>馱哩<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0919c21" ed="T"/>怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>路<note place="inline">引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>路吉&CB00135;輸羅播<note place="inline">引</note>尼&CB00135;囉乞
<lb n="0919c22" ed="T"/>叉<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00805;<note place="inline">切身</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>尾&CB00135;用<note place="inline">二合</note>婆曳<note place="inline">引</note>毘
<lb n="0919c23" ed="T"/>藥<note place="inline">二合</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0919c24" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919c2401">爾時聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩在大眾中。即從
<lb n="0919c25" ed="T"/>座起合掌向佛。白佛言世尊。我於此正法。亦
<lb n="0919c26" ed="T"/>說擁護真言章句。</p>
<lb n="0919c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0919c2701" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>尾曩<note place="inline">引</note>舍&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>怛也<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0919c28" ed="T"/>體迦&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>怛也<note place="inline">二合</note>彌怛哩<note place="inline">二合</note>輸弟目訖
<lb n="0919c29" ed="T"/>帝<note place="inline">二合</note>尾摩&CB00619;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">引</note>娑迦<note place="inline">二合</note>哩<note place="inline">引</note>桉
<pb n="0920a" id="T21.1403.0920a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0920a01" ed="T"/>拏哩<note place="inline">引</note>半拏哩<note place="inline">引</note>濕尾<note place="inline">二合引</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>半拏囉&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>悉
<lb n="0920a02" ed="T"/>&CB00135;麼<note place="inline">引</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>迦囉<note place="inline">引</note>羅迦閉羅賓&CB00344;羅<note place="inline">引</note>乞史
<lb n="0920a03" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>那地目乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>囉乞史<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0920a04" ed="T"/>&CB00805;<note place="inline">切身引</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note>羅沒哩<note place="inline">二合</note>底喻<note place="inline">二合</note>婆
<lb n="0920a05" ed="T"/>曳<note place="inline">引</note>毘藥<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note>彌<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00425;舍滿<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00418;薩哩&CB00085;
<lb n="0920a06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>迦<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0920001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【明】</note><app n="0920001"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">囉</rdg></app>沒哩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline"><note n="0920002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">入＝引【明】</note><app n="0920002"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">引</rdg></app></note>阿哩也
<lb n="0920a07" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>&CB00085;路<note place="inline">引</note>吉帝<note place="inline">引</note>濕&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉帝<note place="inline">引</note>惹<note n="0920003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娑＝婆【明】</note><app n="0920003"><lem wit="【大】">娑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">婆</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>娑
<lb n="0920a08" ed="T"/>&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0920a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920a0901">爾時祕密主金剛手菩薩。往詣佛前合掌頂
<lb n="0920a10" ed="T"/>禮。白佛言世尊。我今於此正法之中。亦說陀
<lb n="0920a11" ed="T"/>羅尼真言章句。</p>
<lb n="0920a12" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920a1201" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>母&CB00135;母&CB00135;母&CB00135;摩帝母&CB00135;摩
<lb n="0920a13" ed="T"/>帝蘇摩帝摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>摩帝賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>摩帶
<lb n="0920a14" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>哩曩<note place="inline">二合引</note>悉底<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>播<note place="inline">引</note>半&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0920a15" ed="T"/>播<note place="inline">引</note>尼囉憾涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>茶娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0920a16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920a1601">世尊我此陀羅尼。名無能勝擁護有情。若人
<lb n="0920a17" ed="T"/>書寫憶念。所有一切恐怖及其中夭悉令解
<lb n="0920a18" ed="T"/>脫。</p>
<lb n="0920a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920a1901">爾時大梵天王索訶世界主。白佛言世尊。我
<lb n="0920a20" ed="T"/>為利益一切眾生。於此正法亦說陀羅尼真
<lb n="0920a21" ed="T"/>言章句。</p>
<lb n="0920a22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920a2201" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>呬&CB00619;彌&CB00619;唧&CB00619;娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0920a23" ed="T"/>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩<note place="inline">二合</note>布哩<note place="inline">引</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩
<lb n="0920a24" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>尼<note place="inline">引</note>沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>憾摩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00344;哩鼻<note place="inline">二合引</note>補瑟波
<lb n="0920a25" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合</note>設娑哆<note place="inline">二合</note>哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0920004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">賀＋（引）【明】</note><app n="0920004"><lem wit="【大】">賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">賀引</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0920a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920a2601">世尊我此陀羅尼名梵天杖。擁護一切有情。
<lb n="0920a27" ed="T"/>遠離中夭不生恐怖亦能除滅一切罪業。爾
<lb n="0920a28" ed="T"/>時帝釋天主。詣佛前立合掌頂禮。白佛言世
<lb n="0920a29" ed="T"/>尊。我今於此正法。亦說陀羅尼真言章<note n="0920005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">句＋（曰）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0920005"><lem wit="【大】">句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">句曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<pb n="0920b" id="T21.1403.0920b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0920b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920b0101" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">引</note>沒馱麼<note place="inline">引</note>旦膩<note place="inline">引</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;&CB00135;憍
<lb n="0920b02" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引</note>哩巘<note place="inline">引</note>馱<note place="inline">引</note>哩贊拏&CB00619;摩<note place="inline">引</note>鄧詣布訖&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0920b03" ed="T"/>悉娑<note place="inline">引</note>羅沒囉<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>呬曩末馱用<note place="inline">二合</note>哆羅
<lb n="0920b04" ed="T"/>尼滿&CB00418;<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00619;&CB00135;計<note place="inline">引</note>作迦<note n="0920006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＝羅【三】</note><note n="0920006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉＝羅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0920006"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;<note place="inline">引</note>枳舍&CB00085;
<lb n="0920b05" ed="T"/>哩舍<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00085;哩娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></p>
<lb n="0920b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920b0601">世尊我此陀羅尼名金剛座。解脫一切怖畏。
<lb n="0920b07" ed="T"/>遠離一切中夭。</p>
<lb n="0920b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920b0801">爾時持國天王增長天王廣目天王多聞天王
<lb n="0920b09" ed="T"/>俱詣佛前合掌頂禮。白佛言世尊。我等於此
<lb n="0920b10" ed="T"/>正法。亦說陀<note n="0920007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔羅〕－【明】</note><app n="0920007"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>尼真言章句。</p>
<lb n="0920b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920b1101" type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他補瑟閉<note place="inline">二合引</note>蘇補瑟閉<note place="inline">二合引</note>度波
<lb n="0920b12" ed="T"/>波哩賀<note place="inline">引</note>哩<note place="inline">引</note>阿<note place="inline">引</note>哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉<note place="inline">二合</note>設悉帝
<lb n="0920b13" ed="T"/><note place="inline">二合引</note>扇<note place="inline">引</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00135;哩目<note place="inline">二合</note>訖帝<note place="inline">二合引</note>夢&CB00344;&CB00619;曳<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0920b14" ed="T"/>合</note>呬囉拏也<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00344;哩鼻<note place="inline">二合引</note>娑&CB00418;<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>娑
<lb n="0920b15" ed="T"/>哆<note place="inline">二合</note>尾帝<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0920b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920b1601">世尊我等四大天王作說陀羅尼名為無怖。
<lb n="0920b17" ed="T"/>於其恐怖能施無畏。遠離中夭增延壽命。</p>
<lb n="0920b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0920b1801">爾時復有大海龍王。所謂大意龍王雷光龍
<lb n="0920b19" ed="T"/>王。無熱惱龍王電舌龍王百光龍王。俱詣佛
<lb n="0920b20" ed="T"/>所合掌頂禮白佛言世尊。我有陀羅尼名如
<lb n="0920b21" ed="T"/>意寶。擁護有情。若人書寫讀誦。能除一切雷
<lb n="0920b22" ed="T"/>電怖畏。一切中夭一切諸毒一切惡病。及不
<lb n="0920b23" ed="T"/>吉祥鬼神亦不得便。世尊若持此真言。我等
<lb n="0920b24" ed="T"/>龍類悉皆悲愍不生嫉&CB00107;。於意云何龍趣之
<lb n="0920b25" ed="T"/>類行嫉&CB00107;心。若聞此法而無嫉&CB00107;。陀羅尼曰。</p>
